      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a showroom-quality E46 M3, a definitive analog masterpiece. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example has undergone extensive preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Beisan components, rod bearing replacement, and a proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension has been subtly enhanced with Bilstein PSS10 adjustable coilovers for superior damping control without compromising the chassis's inherent balance. Finished in pristine paint with a factory-correct interior, this vehicle represents the zenith of BMW M-division engineering, free of any mechanical or cosmetic defects.",
      "price": 48500.0,
